
# BOB - The smart punchball
- Author: Alexandros Gounis
---
### BOB (Android app)

1. *`Clone this repository`*
2. *`Download Android Studio:`* (https://developer.android.com/studio)
3.*`Build and run the app`*

---

### BOB Arduino (arduino code)

1. *`Connect device to usb`*
2. *`Download & Open arduino IDE`* ([https://www.arduino.cc/en/Main/Software](https://www.arduino.cc/en/Main/Software))
3.*`Upload the project to Arduino:`*
- try the testing utility first

---
